				<mouse class="tooltip-small linkBlue">(?)<span>原版的固定300，改为自信值的40倍。</span></mouse>
			</label>
		</div>
		<div class="settingsToggle">
			<label>
				<<checkbox "$options.bjx_averymoney" false true autocheck>>
