				<mouse class="tooltip-small linkBlue">(?)<span>并非是狗舍声望，而是好感。</span></mouse>
			</label>
		</div>
		<div class="settingsToggle">
			<label>
				<<checkbox "$options.bjx_crimewipe" false true autocheck>>
